  <brief_title>Remimazolam Phase II Cardiac Anesthesia Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Single-blind Phase II Study Evaluating the Efficacy, Safety and Pharmacokinetics of Remimazolam in General Anesthesia in Adult Patients Undergoing Cardiac Surgery, Including Follow-up Sedation in the PACU/ICU</official_title>
